WEBVTT

00:02:57.960 --> 00:03:03.896
(Laughter)

00:03:03.920 --> 00:03:06.520
The thing is, you know, I love sleeping.

00:03:07.160 --> 00:03:10.896
And when I sleep, I really
prefer to do it while spooning.

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:14.856
I've been spooning on almost a pro level
for close to 20 years,

00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:17.776
but in all this time,
I've never figured out

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:19.456
what to do with that bottom arm.

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:22.096
(Laughter)

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:24.056
(Applause)

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:26.360
And the only thing --

00:03:27.640 --> 00:03:30.496
the only thing that makes sleeping
even more complicated